# Lattice: vendored solver artifacts (fetched locally, not committed)
lattice/vendor/*.jar
lattice/vendor/*.class
lattice/vendor/jdk

# Lattice: elicitation sessions & solver output. Unanchored on purpose — the elicit-spec skill
# runs the CLI from lattice/ with `--session ../.lattice-session-<slug>/`, so sessions land at the
# repo ROOT, which the old `lattice/`-anchored pattern never matched. Phase 0b scratch sessions go
# to mktemp -d and never land in the tree at all; the pattern below is a backstop for the ones that
# predate that, or that get pointed here by hand.
.lattice-session*/
.lattice-scratch*/
lattice/_apalache-out/

# Tooling scratch
.superpowers/
